data.description: Back on the market due to no fault of Seller   The possibilities are endless! The "Carolina II" floorplan will make you say "Wow!" from the moment you enter the two story foyer! The main floor features front living room, formal dining, huge eat-in kitchen overlooking great room and private office that could serve as a 5th bedroom or in-law room on the main floor! Lots of natural light cascades throughout! Full bathroom on the main floor is great for guests! Situated on private fenced lot backing up to wooded area, this home also has a covered porch - outdoor retreat! Gourmet kitchen with pantry, stainless appliances, granite counters and beautiful stained cabinets - great place to gather! The spacious second story has a master bedroom that is like having two rooms in one with its own sitting area and a big master closet that could be another room in itself!. Large bedroom on the second story can also serve as a media room! If you are looking for a home that has it all, you have found it! Welcome Home!
